{"tid":393524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好想改變呢個世界","createTime":"2017-09-09T10:26:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-20T03:20:55.000Z","uid":1735,"like":196,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d9be34c6ccf163fbf4a7f9459bd9094405e72a95","tid":393524,"uid":1735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T10:26:51.000Z","msg":"呢兩日發生嘅事，已經令我覺得呢個世界痴咗線。<br />\n<br />\n我都覺得恭喜人哋死仔係有啲口臭、過份，但未至於要俾人公開批鬥呀嘛。開記招播cctv強烈譴責哽咽，呢啲本來只會喺hea9政治show同警方搵通緝犯會岀現嘅事，竟然會一齊發生喺批鬥兩個學生身上，原因就係因為佢地口臭。<br />\n<br />\n有人跳樓電視訪問竟然唔係慰問，而係討論下樓價會點跌。轉頭就企喺道德高地話人哋恭喜人死仔係涼薄，要不得。<br />\n<br />\n我好憤怒，同時亦都好有無力感。香港人唔係好自豪自己嘅法治民主自由嘅咩，依家連口臭下都俾人批鬥，都係會無人關心，仲會話嗰兩個學生抵死。越大權力嘅人就越無能，我終於明點解。<br />\n<br />\n我想去改變呢個世界，令大家重新擁抱引以為傲嘅民主自由，令呢班痴線同荼毒社會嘅淤泥永遠消失。但現實係，我無嘢做到，甚至連改變我老豆睇東x報呢個習慣都做唔到。<br />\n<br />\n我諗我明夜神月有死亡筆記時嘅諗法係咩了。"},{"pid":"b454760d66751e815435ca33a9d4b8c1de49a9b6","tid":393524,"uid":1735,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T10:28:06.000Z","msg":"係咪真係要世界末日/ 透露戰爭重新洗牌先會改變到現狀"},{"pid":"a3f963eb9c1c50f980312e65375a9497fbe4ab3f","tid":393524,"uid":1735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T10:31:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8222fb2bf2731e0699b10b73bf9cd4584999c955","tid":393524,"uid":14103,"like":30,"dislike":3,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T10:33:09.000Z","msg":"如果冇每日150個<br />\n冇支那學生<br />\n冇單雙非<br />\n冇支那人 其實好多問題都唔存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33656572960c7749d1f2cc125cb78fb8b7f0b0bd","tid":393524,"uid":120753,"like":1,"dislike":19,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T10:34:03.000Z","msg":"又系度ff<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f9a0aa4f8f5dbb028dd52c25467d52cd8eacd36","tid":393524,"uid":1735,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T10:36:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果冇每日150個<br />\n冇支那學生<br />\n冇單雙非<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">冇支那人</span> 其實好多問題都唔存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個根本係社會扭曲嘅根源"},{"pid":"950ca7f0aa10d82c329ecfbb6453ad61e934906c","tid":393524,"uid":1735,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T10:36:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又系度ff<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講下自己諗法啫"},{"pid":"46ef9c8f856f029b9b3857d317f69167489e035a","tid":393524,"uid":39215,"like":2,"dislike":16,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T10:36:36.000Z","msg":"番工啦 死毒撚"},{"pid":"a6171687402ce316fab349212b918e0133401c5c","tid":393524,"uid":1735,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T10:39:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>番工啦 死毒撚</blockquote><br />\n係咪就係因為返工先令到你對呢個社會咁冷漠？認為只要無阻到你返工就得？你有無撫心自問，真係想一世做人奴才幫人搵錢？最後到七老八十回想起自己做過啲咩，你會發覺，係無，只係一名奴才，到死嗰日都係。"},{"pid":"e572d4e25af3de04910f2fbf06cc6b20021437e2","tid":393524,"uid":15353,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T10:42:08.000Z","msg":"所以樓豬有咩大計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有咩實事做出黎睇下"},{"pid":"f989535e8bbe07c1ce0eaca905cec0dfc1a7b88d","tid":393524,"uid":1735,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T10:47:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所以樓豬有咩大計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有咩實事做出黎睇下</blockquote><br />\n只係有個萌牙嘅念頭，實事我相信好多人都做緊。"},{"pid":"e2d031357dba4e63073fdf8a792a843bb9f8196a","tid":393524,"uid":35693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T10:48:00.000Z","msg":"需要一本死亡筆記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df170a1a13607f2d8885d96901d2c50c1ad37993","tid":393524,"uid":1735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T10:49:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>需要一本死亡筆記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n只可惜呢個只係二次元先會發生嘅事"},{"pid":"bd80a44c1bf0810be341a12